%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^CIRCLES%^RESET%^

Druids gain their powers from the natural forces of the world, and likewise tend to and support those forces whenever possible. Druids organize themselves into conclaves or Circles, dedicated to a specific aspect of nature.

%^ORANGE%^%^ULINE%^Druidic Circles currently available:%^RESET%^

 * %^GREEN%^Circle of Winter
 * %^GREEN%^Circle of Wildfire
 * %^GREEN%^Circle of Pestilence
 * %^GREEN%^Circle of the Claw
 * %^GREEN%^Circle of Wild Growth

Each circle has an individual help file. For example: %^ORANGE%^<help circle of wildfire>%^RESET%^.

%^CYAN%^See also:%^RESET%^ druid, *circles, individual circle files